text.tspan: Icon Template following elementary OS Guidelines
Please follow the dotted suggestions while making your icon,
and don't forget to make the shadow starting from 2px above
the blue line to 1px above the grayish edge.
At the end, go to Layers (Ctrl+Shift+L) and hide, clicking on the
eye symbols the following layers: Grid, Template.
Then save and go see your work on Icon Previewer.
